{
  "stem": "17308.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 122.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the bar mitzvah was combined celebration with their wedding.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, the whole family was there plus quite a lot of guests.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It would be too long to describe because they were quite a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You had a big extended family?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Your father had brothers and sisters and--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, my father had a brother, two sisters.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother, they had also few sisters and brother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, we had a lot of friends.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, originally my family comes from Lithuania, Russia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then-- I wouldn't say everybody was there, but at least the close family was there, plus many friends.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was in a small home in Antwerp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, my brother was at the bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really, not really.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well speak about politics, but the truth is they didn't take an active part in politics.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, oh, of course it's everybody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were all upset about it, when it started, because the country was put on alert.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not, I'm afraid, not it help much but anyhow it was an alert already started 1939 already, and everybody was upset.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, there was anti-Semitism in Belgium like in any other country, I would imagine.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were some Flemish movements what were extreme right, and they were anti-Semitic, but I wouldn't say it was on an unbearable scale.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a movement.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not personally.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they were all mostly Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had a few friends who were not Jewish but the majority was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, friends were mostly Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Here and there there's some business relation where they are not Jewish, but I would say we circulate in circles which were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In general, it was good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I understand that it changed only war time, when I wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
